{"tid":2002453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[510 九龍見] 與其單單打打 不如分化香港再出發大聯盟","createTime":"2020-05-05T07:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T13:24:51.000Z","uid":200663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8a60f60731f4c7d980a4bbaef32340caca106a","tid":2002453,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"最近誠哥就加盟咗 香港再出發大聯盟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人為咗誠哥係咪黃絲而爭拗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上佢係咪黃絲關我鬼事咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係知道藍絲自從 網開一面論 後<br />\n都當佢係黃絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然有個所謂黃絲入咗聯盟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就梗係要分化啦</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以上藍絲文宣 channel 宣傳下呢個聯盟<br />\n表面想再出發 實際係想出發去陰間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等呢個聯盟兩面不討好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時都可以出個聯盟成員嘅柒事文宣<br />\n令大家唔信佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b682d2be78ef9cad7baf1921fca4d65f29e51c07","tid":2002453,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1cb387210645662687524a38f8c792502fdf7d","tid":2002453,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"這個大聯盟其實是想架空政府 對抗中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807d829203308df484673e961875202bf1102bbd","tid":2002453,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1cb387210645662687524a38f8c792502fdf7d","tid":2002453,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep